objet.",{"type":28,"tag":389,"props":1324,"children":1325},{},[],{"type":33,"value":1327},"\nUne bonne conception permet une bonne modularité et une grande souplesse, tout ce qui est nécessaire à la testabilité.",{"type":28,"tag":29,"props":1329,"children":1330},{},[1331,1333,1343],{"type":33,"value":1332},"C'est d'ailleurs parce que la testabilité impose une programmation plus rigoureuse que certaines méthodes de développement impose d'écrire les tests en premiers (Voir ",{"type":28,"tag":36,"props":1334,"children":1337},{"href":1335,"rel":1336},"http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test_Driven_Development",[40],[1338,1340],{"type":33,"value":1339},"TDD",{"type":28,"tag":608,"props":1341,"children":1342},{"alt":7,"src":610},[],{"type":33,"value":667},{"type":28,"tag":804,"props":1345,"children":1347},{"width":1346},36,[1348],{"type":28,"tag":823,"props":1349,"children":1350},{},[1351],{"type":28,"tag":827,"props":1352,"children":1353},{},[1354,1359],{"type":28,"tag":831,"props":1355,"children":1356},{"vAlign":833},[1357],{"type":33,"value":1358}," ",{"type":28,"tag":831,"props":1360,"children":1361},{},[1362],{"type":33,"value":1358},{"type":28,"tag":29,"props":1364,"children":1365},{},[1366],{"type":33,"value":1367},"Sur un code ancien n'ayant pas été conçu pour être testable, l'application des solutions ci-dessus permet de rendre progressivement testable le logiciel.",{"type":28,"tag":53,"props":1369,"children":1371},{"id":1370},"sources",[1372],{"type":33,"value":1373},"Sources",{"type":28,"tag":65,"props":1375,"children":1376},{},[1377,1389,1401,1413],{"type":28,"tag":69,"props":1378,"children":1379},{},[1380],{"type":28,"tag":36,"props":1381,"children":1384},{"href":1382,"rel":1383},"http://blog.o2sources.com/2009/03/23/celui-qui-voulait-ecrire-du-code-testable.html",[40],[1385,1386],{"type":33,"value":1382},{"type":28,"tag":608,"props":1387,"children":1388},{"alt":7,"src":610},[],{"type":28,"tag":69,"props":1390,"children":1391},{},[1392],{"type":28,"tag":36,"props":